TITLE: Adding casdoorRegister Method to SysLoginService
DESCRIPTION: This Java code adds the `casdoorRegister` method to the `SysLoginService`. This method registers a new user in the RuoYi-Cloud database using the provided Casdoor username.  It creates a new `SysUser` object and uses the `remoteUserService` to register the user.
