TITLE: Web Page for Displaying Protected Resources
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet defines a Thymeleaf template for displaying the protected resources (Foos). It displays a table of Foos with their IDs and names.  It also shows the authenticated user's name using Spring Security's `sec:authentication` tag.
SOURCE: https://github.com/casdoor/casdoor-website/blob/master/docs/integration/java/spring-security/spring-security-oauth.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
