SOURCE: https://github.com/casdoor/casdoor-website/blob/master/docs/integration/java/spring-security/spring-security-oauth.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
public class FooModel {
        private Long id;
        private String name;

        public FooModel(Long id, String name) {
            super();
            this.id = id;
            this.name = name;
        }
        public Long getId() {
            return id;
        }
        public void setId(Long id) {
            this.id = id;
        }
        public String getName() {
            return name;
        }
        public void setName(String name) {
            this.name = name;
        }
    }
```

